The pypi project page of keras-application https://pypi.org/project/Keras-Applications/

body:
The `keras_application` module is available as `keras-application` pip package. Which is also automatically installed when install using `pip install -U keras`
The pypi project page of keras-application `https://pypi.org/project/Keras-Applications/`
